4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential skills in JavaScript and Python over an 18-week period. The program includes three classes weekly with a low student-to-teacher ratio (1:7), ensuring personalized attention. No prior coding experience is required, making it accessible for beginners. Students learn to build websites, utilize APIs, and develop functional applications. The course culminates in a personal project, providing hands-on experience and a Full-Stack Developer certificate upon completion. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop